title: A Seat at the Table with Anthony Bourdain (Part 1)
description: How can a dish be fit for a king in one country and for the garbage in another? Find out when Neil deGrasse Tyson sits down with world traveler, author and chef Anthony Bourdain.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
